                    <app loc="line 2"><note>ΗΡΑΚΕΙΟΣ is quite clear on the stone (so Ansaldi, correctly).</note></app>
                    <app loc="line 3"><note>Only a cross-bar is visible on the stone for the T, mid-line.</note></app>
